from typing import *
def f_gold(s: str, p: str, removable: List[int]) -> int:
    def check(k):
        i = j = 0
        ids = set(removable[:k])
        while i < m and j < n:
            if i not in ids and s[i] == p[j]:
                j += 1
            i += 1
        return j == n
    m, n = len(s), len(p)

    while left < right:
        mid = (left + right + 1) >> 1
        if check(mid):
            left = mid
        else:
            right = mid - 1
    return left
